data.description: Beautiful contemporary style home perfect for your family.  The amazing two-story ceiling height first floor offers a Bedroom in the back (currently used as a family room), front living room with oversized windows that invite the outside in and an amazing gas fireplace for your family enjoyment, dining room and an open concept kitchen with stainless steel appliances, on the second floor the home offers two Bedrooms PLUS a LARGE LOFT and the second full bathroom.  The first floor "bonus room/bedroom" offers space for a home office, bedroom or just an easy retreat, family room area.  The home includes a "high-tech-green" technology system which is basically an advanced on-site waste- water treatment system.  Recent enhancement in the home are new Stainless-steel appliances and washer and dryer, new driveway, new well pump, new water softener that stays, new carpet in the stairs and new cooling and heating system in the back bedroom. The septic tank was cleaned recently as well.
